/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: mps_SASTAV_ORGANIZACIONE_JEDINICE */
/*==============================================================*/
create table mps_SASTAV_ORGANIZACIONE_JEDINICE
(
PS_ID integer not null,
VO_OZNAKA char(2) not null,
DR_IDENTIFIKATOR char(3) not null,
NM_DENTIFIKATOR integer not null,
OJ_IDENTIFIKATOR integer not null,
MPS_PS_ID integer not null,
MPS_VO_OZNAKA char(2) not null,
MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR char(3) not null,
MPS_NM_DENTIFIKATOR integer not null,
MPS_OJ_IDENTIFIKATOR integer not null,
constraint PK_MPS_SASTAV_ORGANIZACIONE_JE primary key clustered (MPS_PS_ID, PS_ID, MPS_VO_OZNAKA, VO_OZNAKA, DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, NM_DENTIFIKATOR, OJ_IDENTIFIKATOR, MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, MPS_NM_DENTIFIKATOR, MPS_OJ_IDENTIFIKATOR)
);

);
